BUILD DEPENDENCIES

- unix-like environment: rm, dd, sleep, timeout, ...
- gnumake
- SDCC >= v4.2.0
- hex2bin

TEST DEPENDENCIES

- sage-etcher/nsae

BUILD

    make

BUILD OUTPUT FILES

- src/**.com
- src/**.bin

INSTALL HELLORLD.BIN TO NS-ADV DISKETTE (DSDD, load BIN into sectors 4-8)

    ./tools/extract_bootloader.sh hellorld_disk.nsi src/hellorld/hellorld.bin

